  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Study will look at ability of fluoride varnish to remineralize white spot enamel lesions that
      can occur around the edge of fixed orthodontic brackets.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      To determine the efficacy of 5% sodium fluoride varnish with tricalcium phosphate in
      reverting white spot lesions after fixed orthodontic treatment, compared with a fluoride gel.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
